'''铋化物'''是含Bi<sup>3-</sup>[[阴离子|阴离子]]的[[化合物|化合物]]。[[碱金属|碱金属]]的铋化物M<sub>3</sub>Bi都是已知的，例如铋化钠（Na<sub>3</sub>Bi）可以由[[钠|钠]]和[[铋|铋]]的单质在高温、高压下反应得到。<ref>S. A. Kulinich, M. E. Leonova, L. G. Sevast’yanova, ''et al''. [https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Sergei_Kulinich/publication/271215281_High-Pressure_Synthesis_of_Sodium_Bismuthide_Na_3_Bi/links/54c2c3240cf256ed5a8f84ec.pdf High-Pressure Synthesis of Sodium Bismuthide Na<sub>3</sub>Bi] {{Wayback|url=https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Sergei_Kulinich/publication/271215281_High-Pressure_Synthesis_of_Sodium_Bismuthide_Na_3_Bi/links/54c2c3240cf256ed5a8f84ec.pdf |date=20170217062632 }}. ''Russian Journal of General Chemistry'', 1999. 69（5）: 681-683</ref>

多元铋化物也有文献报道，例如有着PbClF结构的KCaBi<ref>H. Hirt, H. J. Deiseroth. [https://www.degruyter.com/downloadpdf/j/ncrs.2003.218.issue-jg/ncrs.2003.218.jg.5/ncrs.2003.218.jg.5.pdf Crystal structure of potassium calcium bismuthide, KCaBi] {{Wayback|url=https://www.degruyter.com/downloadpdf/j/ncrs.2003.218.issue-jg/ncrs.2003.218.jg.5/ncrs.2003.218.jg.5.pdf |date=20170217142702 }}. ''Zeitschrift für Kristallographie'', 2003. 218(JG)</ref>、同时含有-1和-3价Bi的化合物Ba<sub>2</sub>Cd<sub>2.13</sub>Bi<sub>3</sub>O<ref>S.-Q. Xia and S. Bobev. [http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?WM2421 Dibarium tricadmium bis­muthide(-I,-III) oxide, Ba<sub>2</sub>Cd<sub>3</sub>Bi<sub>3-δ</sub>O] {{Wayback|url=http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?WM2421 |date=20190701185000 }}. ''Acta Cryst''. (2010). E66, i81 DOI: 10.1107/S1600536810046283</ref>等。
